  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FlipScapes</strong> blends classic pinball with energetic arcade action, from <strong>pachinko</strong> and <strong>brick-breaking</strong> to <strong>whack-a-mole</strong> and beyond. Ramps, rails, bumpers and spinning targets shape each playfield. Choose a hero with a signature ability and launch into an adventure across the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From underwater wonders to scorching deserts, to the vastness of outer space, you'll bounce, flip and slide!  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/e75391562da35723e21bcebff7c92f1f.poster.avif?t=1767898479\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/e75391562da35723e21bcebff7c92f1f.webm?t=1767898479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/6705a0d5097def0a8049341e597992cc.avif?t=1767898479\" width=515 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Callisto, a curious cutie who is always on the lookout for new places to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/6e25d2229fca47cc879dd53702bf11ac.avif?t=1767898479\" width=515 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rage flip through the playfield with Tuhin, blow up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/2f4a985a9bb918cddd13f970532b6686.avif?t=1767898479\" width=515 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cronus bends time itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/0ea0d626efa80f099ea5891203e54567.avif?t=1767898479\" width=515 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the magic of flower power with Aspen and her overpowered ability.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/da549f2ec3d33b7473e4e03e992044a1.avif?t=1767898479\" width=515 height=116 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aukai has the ability to call upon his fish companions for assistance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><br>Fast-paced 2D minigames</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/fb34b8fd7237efeeb56ec26184f31ff4.poster.avif?t=1767898479\" width=759 height=349 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/fb34b8fd7237efeeb56ec26184f31ff4.webm?t=1767898479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mystical Genie will guide you on your pinball pachinko journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/d3ef4a018e5cf9a1f7c4aba15da671e0.poster.avif?t=1767898479\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/d3ef4a018e5cf9a1f7c4aba15da671e0.webm?t=1767898479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play characters with unique active and passive powers. Level up!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover multiple worlds with their own stories that you can explore with your chosen hero.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack and reactive music while playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast off to the celestial heights of the leaderboards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements such as \"Win 5 level using only the left flipper\" and \"Ace Score\" for levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great on Steam Deck and full controller support.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to check out the <strong>Downloadable Soundtrack!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Notes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game uses Epic Online Services (EOS). You can play <strong>Offline</strong> if you want. However, playing <strong>Online</strong> enables cloud save, achievements & leaderboards.</p></li></ul>",
