d.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/d3ef4a018e5cf9a1f7c4aba15da671e0.poster.avif?t=1767898479\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2176580/extras/d3ef4a018e5cf9a1f7c4aba15da671e0.webm?t=1767898479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play characters with unique active and passive powers. Level up!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover multiple worlds with their own stories that you can explore with your chosen hero.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack and reactive music while playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast off to the celestial heights of the leaderboards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements such as \"Win 5 level using only the left flipper\" and \"Ace Score\" for levels.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great on Steam Deck and full controller support.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to check out the <strong>Downloadable Soundtrack!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Notes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game uses Epic Online Services (EOS). You can play <strong>Offline</strong> if you want. However, playing <strong>Online</strong> enables cloud save, achievements & leaderboards.</p></li></ul>",
